{"tid":953394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【來生不做..】大陸狗被中國棄養   移民美國重新做狗","createTime":"2018-12-24T02:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T07:05:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"15060fb10ae657cf653a00deb3a26c0ead54f36e","tid":953394,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181218/large/1545063037_e5da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181218%2Flarge%2F1545063037_e5da.jpg&h=faefb109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國五頭被棄養的寵物犬，獲美國動物志願組織「Rescue Gang」收養，於周六晚抵達威斯康辛州最大城巿密爾沃基（Milwaukee）。<br />\n<br />\n「Rescue Gang」負責人Aloura Pearson表示，中國雖然有狗肉巿場，但今次獲救的五頭寵物犬、包括三頭金毛尋回犬，全部被主人棄養，不曾面臨被屠宰厄運。<br />\n<br />\nPearson指出，中國大量繁殖寵物，拋棄動物問題嚴重。她表示，中國缺乏動物收容所或動物志願機構，很多旅居中國的外國人，都在當地設立動物收容所，但鮮為當地人所知，導致很多動物流浪街頭，或被拋棄在獸醫診所。<br />\n<br />\n今次「移民」美國的五頭狗隻，在中國獸醫轉介下，被「Rescue Gang」帶走。Pearson表示，它們經獸醫檢查後，將供人領養。<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181218/59041891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59041891&d=JcB2XAMnINmnq8cHyxjvOsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=71eaa843\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59041891&h=51589005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181218/59041891</a>"},{"pid":"25c67a0c5e0a10addcb39273d877d7f5aa2016c2","tid":953394,"uid":24104,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:09:40.000Z","msg":"會唔會有原主人出黎相認，再申請入籍美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eedc6df10da2b6a983ad013755d79a1920f1b75","tid":953394,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"reply